title: Silver player looking for a team
body:
Hi, I'm looking to join a ranked team. Preferrably with Silver+ players :)
Silver IV
support>mid>adc>jungle>top.

replies.body: Silver V and still climbing. Mid main but can play any other role except adc. Also looking for a team to help towards improving myself and others. IGN Qwertyuiopman. CastielZaim you're also welcome to add me if you're interested. I do have skype.

Ay man, I'm looking to start a ranked team once iv got enough players, I'm currently in Bronze 3 and want to climb but with a team that isn't salty or toxic. If ya don't mind playing with a less experienced player thats a quick learner, then hit us up if you're keen to join. IGN: CastielZaim11
